    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_34_11",
    "text": "(1)位置，位于喜马拉雅山南面的印度次大陆上，酒积约3厄平方干米。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
